# <footer>

# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci
# Subject should be imperative and under 50 characters
# Body should explain WHY not WHAT (code shows what)
# Footer: Closes/Fixes #issue_number or Co-Authored-By:
#
# Example:
#   feat: Add OCR fallback for dialog detection
#
#   Implement Vision Framework integration for dialogs that don't expose
#   accessibility APIs. This provides fallback detection for proprietary
#   apps and sandboxed applications.
#
#   Closes #123
#   Co-Authored-By: Name <email@example.com>
